<L><HI>I tremble, &amp;c</HI></L>
<L><HI>Hold, hold, &amp;c</HI></L>
<L><HI>On a, &amp;c</HI></L>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fola.</SPEAKER>
<L><HI>Now you're, &amp;c</HI></L>
<L><HI>Nay, leave, &amp;c</HI></L>
<L><HI>I tremble, &amp;c</HI></L>
<L><HI>Hold, hold, &amp;c</HI></L>
<L><HI>On a, &amp;c</HI></L>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Buff.</SPEAKER>
<L><HI>Ye have humbled me&mdash;what would ye fur|ther.</HI></L>
<STAGE>(embracing Davo)</STAGE>
<L><HI>Thanks kind Davo!</HI></L>
</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="44" REF="50">
<SPEAKER>Davo. </SPEAKER>
<STAGE>(with a ludicrous bow)</STAGE>
<P><HI>Sir! your Schiavo!</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Matil. </SPEAKER>
<STAGE>(applauding)</STAGE>
<P><HI>Bravo! bravo!</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Buff. </SPEAKER>
<STAGE>(again embracing Davo)</STAGE>
<P><HI>Gen'rous Davo!</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Ceph.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>Bravo! bravo!</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
